      <title>麦当劳鸡肉“巨无霸”商标在欧盟被取消</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/mcdonald-s-chicken-big-mac-trademark-axed-in-eu-burger-battle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦当劳公司在欧盟失去了其标志性产品“巨无霸”鸡肉汉堡的商标权，因为法官裁定这家快餐巨头未能充分行使独家权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/mcdonald-s-chicken-big-mac-trademark-axed-in-eu-burger-battle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 09:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>温德霍斯特在德国银行法刑事调查中获释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/windhorst-cleared-in-german-criminal-probe-over-banking-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国金融家拉尔斯·温德霍斯特 (Lars Windhorst) 因设立融资工具偿还投资公司 H2O Asset Management 而违反银行规则，德国对此展开刑事调查，最终被判无罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/windhorst-cleared-in-german-criminal-probe-over-banking-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 08:20:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
