    <item>
      <title>莫迪的选举挫折对一些全球股票基金来说只是昙花一现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/modi-s-election-setback-only-a-blip-for-some-global-stock-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于许多外国投资者来说，印度股市周二暴跌近 4000 亿美元，这正是投资这个他们眼中全球最有前景的经济体之一的又一个机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/modi-s-election-setback-only-a-blip-for-some-global-stock-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 06:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
